    "en": {
      "title": "Special meeting of the ruling party today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It was announced that this meeting will be held at 3.00 pm today in the new building audience hall of the Ministry of Finance.",
        "This is the first time that the ruling party MPs will meet after Ranil Wickremesinghe took office as president.",
        "It has been reported that issues such as the submission and implementation of the Emergency Act in the Parliament and the formation of an all-party government will be discussed. (a)"
      ],
